01:11:57.440 --> 01:12:02.440
Well, if we combine the name Saen Rak with Chomchan,

01:12:03.160 --> 01:12:09.360
how about we call it ‘Chomrak’?

01:12:13.400 --> 01:12:14.240
That’s sweet.

01:12:16.000 --> 01:12:19.440
But why are you putting my farm’s name at the front?

01:12:20.880 --> 01:12:23.640
Because I’m hopelessly down bad for my wifey.

01:12:27.440 --> 01:12:30.400
You’re getting bolder and bolder every day calling me wifey.

01:12:30.880 --> 01:12:31.920
Of course.

01:12:41.400 --> 01:12:42.920
